STAGE 1 – Onboarding
Goal: Collect user profile data
Rules:
- Ask one question at a time
- Do NOT recommend universities
- Do NOT allow shortlisting or locking
- Move to Stage 2 only when profile is complete

STAGE 2 – Discovery
Goal: Explore & shortlist universities
Rules:
- Recommend Dream / Target / Safe universities
- Allow shortlisting
- Do NOT allow locking unless at least one university is shortlisted

STAGE 3 – Locked
Goal: Commitment
Rules:
- Allow locking of ONE university
- Confirm verbally/textually before locking
- Auto-generate application tasks
- Move to Stage 4 immediately after locking

STAGE 4 – Application
Goal: Execution
Rules:
- Manage SOP, Visa, Exam, Document tasks
- Track progress
- Give deadline-based guidance
